{"tid":2091999,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"睇片揭警箍頸撻被告 官促控方查濫暴  骨折司機阻差辦公判罰5,000元","createTime":"2020-07-03T03:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T14:11:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64a8b7125bca14fb3ae797de2b4894e76471bd6f","tid":2091999,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/HSAOVEYQLTQESISWU4VUDY5SAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FHSAOVEYQLTQESISWU4VUDY5SAE%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBKgSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=3fc2026d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FHSAOVEYQLTQESISWU4VUDY5SAE%2F&h=58978743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/HSAOVEYQLTQESISWU4VUDY5SAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n睇片揭警箍頸撻被告 官促控方查濫暴 <br />\n骨折司機阻差辦公判罰5,000元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M_AdfENDR_xpdKPkBkCNKUjbnxw=/945x491/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OMVHJ5HG46GYWUGNQJMRP7RX7Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM_AdfENDR_xpdKPkBkCNKUjbnxw%3D%2F945x491%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOMVHJ5HG46GYWUGNQJMRP7RX7Q.gif&h=aad237dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法官昨指警員當日指被告「搶犯」，顯然與事實不符。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【捉腳救青年】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中年司機途經商場，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n並猛力將他摔下，司機傷勢很大機會由警方造成。裁判官最終判處司機罰款5,000元，<span style=\"color: orange;\">並要求控方跟進警方是否曾經濫用暴力。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據控方案情，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「傷勢超越應得懲罰」<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官徐綺薇昨在庭上觀看辯方呈交、由第三者拍攝的現場片段，隨即質問控方，為何警員將已受控的被告箍頸並大力摔在地上。控方稱警員僅欲分隔被告與張姓青年，徐官聞言反問：<span style=\"color: orange;\">「隔開？箍頸撻落地叫隔開？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_f1Rtc_Q-hjrmpKSlRZkb8JMWl0=/506x593/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VIJVODMVDYGIBOQE2WPGGCLPHY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_f1Rtc_Q-hjrmpKSlRZkb8JMWl0%3D%2F506x593%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVIJVODMVDYGIBOQE2WPGGCLPHY.gif&h=f5a4304f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告關添華（右）因手肘傷勢導致無法工作。<br />\n<br />\n徐官直指從片段中可見，被告未曾有任何舉動，便已遭警員無故摔在地上，其後被告亦沒有任何郁動。控方解釋，當時警員沒為被告扣上手銬，才會如此制服被告，惟徐官認為即使沒上手銬，「都唔應該咁大力」。<br />\n<br />\n徐官判刑時指，被<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n，亦對家人感到愧疚。<br />\n<br />\n徐官續指，被告當時突然走上前對青年有所動作，毫無疑問屬即時反應，並非有預謀犯案；而被告手無寸鐵，盲目衝向全副裝備的防暴警員，亦顯然未經深思熟慮。不過，片段顯示當時有警員捉着被告，並且不斷指被告「搶犯」，警員指控顯然與當時事實不符。另外，被告沒傷害警員，事後亦無人受傷。徐官認為，被告嚴重的傷勢很大機會由警員造成，而非控方所指是因被告猛烈掙扎與警方糾纏所致。被告事後須動手術，影響工作能力及生計，已造成沉重代價，超越他所應得的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC48/20"},{"pid":"3e662cd12b8b297e957ea8bf1c4f39ca050a6bd3","tid":2091999,"uid":68689,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"比黑警整到骨折 仲要判阻差辦公加罰5,000<br />\n黑警就只係要求控方跟進警方是否曾經濫用暴力<br />\n到時一句仲了解緊就咩事都無"},{"pid":"c56e60017b43cc7697eb3a0fee8e403a4be40f42","tid":2091999,"uid":28913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3e662cd12b8b297e957ea8bf1c4f39ca050a6bd3","tid":2091999,"uid":68689,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"比黑警整到骨折 仲要判阻差辦公加罰5,000<br />\n黑警就只係要求控方跟進警方是否曾經濫用暴力<br />\n到時一句仲了解緊就咩事都無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"好過有個廢閪官話自己唔係監警會唔關佢事"},{"pid":"335725e80b075aefeb5491800b55ccf11d46ef6f","tid":2091999,"uid":95221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"告先算"},{"pid":"af5d134be0c4c21e9453184f47430525b7f113c9","tid":2091999,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e662cd12b8b297e957ea8bf1c4f39ca050a6bd3","tid":2091999,"uid":68689,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04